{"tid":1470970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武同和理非其實都一樣","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:51:09.000Z","uid":181240,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f58423efdfef38aa9d813aab48f4c5ce1062794","tid":1470970,"uid":181240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"我地都係香港人<br />\n我地都係因為逃返條例而行出嚟<br />\n因為黑警濫權濫捕而出嚟<br />\n因為爭取5大訴求而出嚟<br />\n<br />\n勇武只係比和理非多一副裝備 多一份勇氣<br />\n脫下裝備你都係和理非<br />\n和理非full gear都可以係勇武<br />\n唔好再講咩818勇武退埸<br />\n無論係咩遊行 只要你有呢5大訴求就請你出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.18見</span><br />\n求你地唔好灰 一定要出嚟"},{"pid":"c6f4889f87fe7cf3d2aa3491c81328a4664be006","tid":1470970,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"勇武 和理非係行為 唔係身分！<br />\n818所以人都要出！ <br />\n嚟多次百萬人大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">816 學界x攬炒團隊遮打大集會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">818 民陣百萬人大遊行 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">819 攬炒xG20團隊全球登報</span>"},{"pid":"4898dae593fd471e378b324f1abb34ba5cb59864","tid":1470970,"uid":181240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"8.18"},{"pid":"53120a501e8742e181ee04034c36bcb03bc7e52f","tid":1470970,"uid":181240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"8.18"},{"pid":"e5d53f374e5cda12b3d90375b7971c36ba965422","tid":1470970,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"係，不用分那麼細"},{"pid":"1397aeea5938bcef1b57eb69729e9e78e0f68606","tid":1470970,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"和理非full gear 係勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c394bf206eee34f2e7b05e951d81dd57